    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This specimen has been maintained to an exacting standard, exhibiting consistent mechanical performance and a well-preserved aesthetic. It represents a premier acquisition for the discerning driver who prioritizes engineering integrity and sustained value. We invite you to experience the refined handling and superior comfort that define this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been so reliable for me and still runs like an absolute dream. It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so while it\u2019s seen a few adventures, it\u2019s still in really solid shape and looks great on the road. It's the perfect fit if you're looking for something dependable and fun to drive without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it handles!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a spine-tingling 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. This example has been mechanically sorted with a recently overhauled VANOS system and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity. The chassis retains its precision with crisp rack-and-pinion steering and a well-damped multi-link rear suspension. While showing honest aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the high-revving individual throttle bodies (ITBs) and recent valve adjustments ensure it performs exactly as Munich intended. A driver-spec icon ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Runs well. Regular oil changes. Minor cosmetic wear only.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained and reliable vehicle that strikes a perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior is finished in a classic coat that still holds a great gloss, showing only minor surface wear and small stone chips typical of careful road use. Inside, you'll find a clean, smoke-free cabin with plush seating that remains firm and supportive; all electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and premium audio system, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in solid health with a documented service history, including a recent fluid flush and a fresh set of all-season tires. It starts up immediately, idles smoothly, and provides a comfortable, confident ride. This is a dependable, high-quality car ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a well-maintained vehicle that exemplifies both durability and refined performance. This model has been curated for the driver who demands consistent reliability without compromising on aesthetic appeal. Featuring a comprehensive service history and a meticulously preserved cabin, it stands as a testament to quality engineering. We invite you to experience the superior handling and sophisticated presence of this distinguished automobile.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
