      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and consistently maintained, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It runs super smoothly and looks great, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
