      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS for optimal power delivery across the rev range. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been maintained with mechanical integrity in mind, including documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering and balanced handling characteristic of this legendary platform. A mechanically sound specimen ready for the curves.",
